{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"ee0f4b2f74","title":"对红线女关于降低山区农村食盐价格来信的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"757dfa074a","index":0,"year":1975,"month":8,"day":13,"articleId":"ee0f4b2f74"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji52","name":"毛泽东全集第52卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/52-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji52":{"comments":[{"id":"6210c5703c","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"粤剧表演艺术家红线女1975年8月5日给毛泽东写信说，最近我到延安、大集、红旗渠参观学习，发现那里的食盐卖得太贵了。太原食盐是一角一分一斤，林县卖一角三分，普阳县桌落大队卖一角六分，其他有的地方还卖到了一角八分。山区的盐比城市贵那么多，我觉得这是对待山区，特别是老解放区的态度问题。像食盐、布匹这类人人不可少的生活必需品，必须照主席历来关心群众生活的教导去办。因此，解野山区的盐价，就是要比城市低廉才对。这封来信和毛泽东的批语，曾作为中共中央1975年9月23日至10月21日召开的农村工作座谈会会议文件印发。"}],"contents":[{"id":"eab4e3cd19","type":"title","text":"对红线女关于降低山区农村食盐价格来信的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74"},{"id":"6210c5703c","type":"paragraph","text":"印发政治局在京各同志，并议一下","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74"},{"id":"9d89773394","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74"},{"id":"eeba503801","type":"paragraph","text":"一九七五年八月十三日","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74"}],"page":{"id":"808a2eb872","publicationId":"maoquanji52","articleId":"ee0f4b2f74","start":56,"end":56}}}},"__N_SSG":true}